'''Grievance Redressal System''' is a mechanism to receive and act on complaints and [[grievance]]s reported by customers of a private organization or public citizens accessing a government (G2C) service.

[[Grievance Redressal]] may be handled directly by organizations through their own [[website]]s or through call centers.  A new innovation is smart [[web portal]]s for grievance processing, connecting customers and action-takers directly through ICT media such as [[Short messaging service|SMS]] and [[email]].

