{{Infobox person | name = Rafael Hertzberg | image = Rafael-Hertzberg.jpg | alt = | caption = Rafael Hertzberg | birth_name = <!-- only use if different from name --> | birth_date = {{birth date|df=yes|1845|9|18}} | birth_place = [[Turku]], [[Grand Duchy of Finland|Finland]] | death_date = {{death date and age|df=yes|1896|12|9|1845|9|18}} | death_place = Helsinki, Finland | nationality = Finnish | other_names = | occupation = writer, translator, historian, businessman, inventor, publicist | years_active = | known_for = [[Julpolska]] lyrics | notable_works = }} {{expand Swedish|date=August 2015}} '''Rafael Hertzberg''' (18 September 1845 in [[Turku]] – 5 December 1896 in [[Helsinki]]) was a [[Swedish-speaking population of Finland|Finland-Swedish]] writer, translator, historian, businessman, inventor and publicist. He is today mostly known for writing the lyrics of the Christmas song ''[[Julpolska]]'' ("Nu ha vi ljus här i vårt hus ...").<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfi.se/sv/svensk-filmdatabas/Item/?type=PERSON&itemid=217038|title=Rafael Hertzberg|publisher=Svensk mediedatabas|language=Swedish|accessdate=27 October 2014}}</ref> He also wrote the [[libretto]] for [[Jean Sibelius]]’ sole opera, ''[[Jungfrun i tornet]]'' (1896).
