{{no footnotes|date=March 2013}}
The '''Wine and Spirit Trade Association''' (WSTA) is the voice of the [[wine]] and [[distilled beverage|spirits]] industry, representing over 345 companies producing, importing and selling wines and spirits. WSTA members range from major [[retailer]]s, [[brand]] owners and [[wholesaler]]s to [[fine wine]] and spirit specialists, [[logistics]] and [[Bottling company|bottling companies]]. 

